tool_description: Team statistics for every NBA team dating back to 1950
title: NBA Team Stats

api_list.name: Team Stats
api_list.description: Provides team stats for the current league year. Optionally, supply a `leagueYear` or `team` parameter to get results for those options.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://nba-team-stats.p.rapidapi.com/teamStats"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "nba-team-stats.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
